    "body": "## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Open a secure page, like wikipedia.org.\r\n2. The CFR for shield icon is displayed.\r\n3. Rotate the device to landscape mode (if you are in portrait mode), or viceversa.\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\nEven if the device is rotated, the CFR's are still displayed.\r\n\r\n### Actual behavior\r\nRotating the device dismisses the CFR.\r\na. However, closing the tab, and opening a new secure page, triggers the CFR for shiled icon again.\r\nb. Regarding the CFR for delete icon, it is not triggerred again.\r\n\r\n### Device information\r\n* Android device: all\r\n* Focus version: Focus Nightly from 2/28\r\n* Shot video regarding the CFR for shield icon:\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/40694158/156129552-ceed0671-927e-4c48-a9d9-f336a26c85bd.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n",
